================================================================================

This project incorporates statistical algorithms and methodologies that are
based on industry-standard practices and may be subject to additional terms:

1. Western Electric Rules: Implementation based on publicly available
   statistical process control methodologies.

2. Statistical Calculations: Process capability indices (Cp, Cpk, Pp, Ppk)
   calculations follow standard statistical formulas and are not subject to
   proprietary restrictions.

3. FDA 21 CFR Part 11 Compliance: Implementation follows published FDA
   guidelines and regulations, which are public domain.

4. Quality Management Standards: Methodologies align with ISO 9001 and other
   international quality standards.

